These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-1::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, vegafina
There 2 different types of food: kiwi, lemon
1. the vegafina-smoker is on the left or right of the baccarat-smoker##3
2. the person eating lemon is on the right of the vegafina-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |   2   |
| Cigar   | vegafina  | baccarat |
| Food       | kiwi | lemon |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-2::.
2 different pets are kept: rabbit, ferret
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: golf, surfing
1. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret##3
2. the owner of the ferret is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2   |
| Pet   | rabbit | ferret |
| Sport      | surfing     | golf  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-3::.
There 2 different types of food: grapes, raspberry
There are 2 different nationalities: french, nigerian
1. the french is on the left of the person eating raspberry##1
2. the french is on the left or right of the person eating raspberry##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Food   | grapes | raspberry  |
| Nationality   | french | nigerian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: fanta, sprite
The people have 2 different jobs:  librarian, journalist
1. the librarian is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
2. the person drinking fanta is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |
| Beverage   | sprite | fanta   |
| Job       | journalist | librarian |

