.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-17::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, roller
The people have 2 different hobbies: dancing, filmmaking
1. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3
2. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |
| Transport    | quad-bike | roller |
| Hobby   | dancing   | filmmaking |

